# Request set for manual testing.
# Works against the local Docker container (docker run -p 8080:8080)
# and against Minikube via: kubectl port-forward svc/demo-micro 8080:9080 -n reto5

### Add two numbers
GET http://localhost:8080/add/5/3

### Subtract two numbers
GET http://localhost:8080/subtract/10/4

### Divide two numbers
GET http://localhost:8080/divide/8/2

### Divide by zero (handled error path)
GET http://localhost:8080/divide/8/0

### Show active external configuration (db.user, db.server)
# Local/Docker: "admin,localhost" (application.properties defaults)
# Minikube:     "admin-k8s,postgres-k8s.reto5.svc.cluster.local" (ConfigMap)
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Actuator health (used by Kubernetes liveness/readiness probes)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
